fields.title: Private Dining
fields.description:
$150.00 per hour with 4 hr minimum plus the cost of supplies and/or groceries with premium ingredients. 

  • 4-course plated meal 
  •  Includes all decor: candles, flowers, linens, china, flatware, glassware, and a bottle of champagne
  • Chef Carolyn and servers are at your disposal. Full setup and breakdown service will provided.
  • Clean and Sanitize Kitchen

*Service charges and sales tax apply

fields.title: Intimate Dinners
fields.description:
Relax, take a load off, and allow us to take you on a culinary journey. Dominique's Dishes will create an amazing dinner party for you while you socialize and mingle with your guests. Enjoy an exquisitely prepared, plated meal that will elevate your dining experience.

  • 4-course plated menu
  • Table set up using your own place settings
  • Bottle Service (if needed)
  • Warm Towel Service
  • Waitstaff Provided
  • Hand Wash and Towel Dry Dishes
  • Clean and Sanitize Kitchen

Rate: Starting at $175 per person (service charges and sales tax are additional)

fields.title: Event Planning
fields.description:
Do you have an upcoming event and need help planning and setting the tone for an exceptional time? No worries! Dominique's Dishes will do the work for you. From decor, themes, budget, and more, Dominique's Dishes will organize the perfect event while creating food from the soul!

Starting at $50 and up

fields.title: Corporate Events
fields.description:
Dominique’s Dishes provides corporate catering for all kinds of business settings, including conferences, training, retreats and off-sites, holiday parties, happy hours, and executive meetings. Dominique’s Dishes will  prepare a gourmet experience that will include set up at your location (disposable utensils, plates & napkins available upon request).

Rate: Starting at $650 plus the cost of food (service charges and sales tax are additional)

fields.title: Meal Prep
fields.description: No time to cook? Dominique’s Dishes is at your service with a meal made to be enjoyed on the go! Prepared meals of prefixed menu selection, or request custom dishes curated just for you. We accommodate most diets. Minimum of 4 meals - down payment requirement. Pick up or third party delivery available. Inquire below for details.

fields.title: Menu Consulting
fields.description:
Need to figure out the 5 w’s of food and menu options (who,what,when, where, and why)? Dominique’s Dishes has the how. Learning why we eat and how we eat can be both daunting and invigorating. Well, worry no more! Have a consultation with chef Carolyn, who has over 20 years of experience. A 7 course dinner meal includes hors d’ oeuvre, soup, appetizer, salad, main course, dessert, and mignardise.

Many cultures enjoy full course meals with a unique assortment of food and customs. Full course meals have a rich, diverse history from many regions that is a result of evolving food trends over time. To the Western world, the full course meal might bring to mind lavish dinner parties or long meals at a fancy restaurant. But how many courses should be in a full course meal, and what should each course consist of? 

Services start at $100 per hour with 2 hr minimum.

fields.title: Chef For A Day
fields.description:
Want to experience the true tantalizing, soul shaking culinary experience in the comfort of your own home or location of your choice?  Reserve Dominique's Dishes “Chef For A Day” service! Perfect for staycations, special occasions (anniversaries, Mother’s & Father’s Day, Family & Friends, teambuilding, etc.) or simply for treating yourself.

  • Breakfast, Lunch, Dinner and Snacks prepared by Chef Carolyn
  • Can also prepare boxed lunches and other food to go as needed
  • Menu Planning and Meal Prep
  • Grocery Shopping
  • Clean and Sanitize Kitchen

Rate: Starting at $1350 plus the cost of groceries (service charges and sales tax are additional)

fields.title: Bon Voyage Chef
fields.description:
Going on vacation? Bring Dominiques Dishes with you. Chef Carolyn will take care of feeding your soul on the road while she travels with you on vacation to prepare delicious meals for your family or group. Bon Voyage chef services include:

  • Grocery Shopping
  • Menu Planning and Meal Prep for trip duration (Customizable based on dietary needs, i.e. vegan,vegetarian,seafood feast, keto, soy free, etc.)
  • Fresh, Home Cooked Meals for Breakfast, Lunch and Dinner for the duration of your stay. Also includes appetizers and snacks
  • Clean and Sanitize Kitchen

Rate: Starting at $1500 per day plus the cost of groceries. Please note that there is a 2-day minimum for Bon Voyage Chef services. Must provide travel and accommodations. (service charges and sales tax are additional)
